lead_paragraph: Henry Burris threw three touchdowns, including one in overtime, and ran in two others as the Ottawa Redblacks stunned the Calgary Stampeders 39-33 to win the 104th Grey Cup in one of the biggest upsets in Canadian Football League history on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: American Football: Burris Leads Redblacks to Grey Cup Win Over Stampeders
